// Self-service subscription RENEWAL — a one-time payment that extends the
// user's CURRENT plan by one billing interval (NOT a new auto-renewing Stripe
// subscription). One row per renewal attempt; `providerRef` is the Stripe
// Checkout Session id (Stripe rail) or the Alipay outTradeNo (CN rail) and is
// the idempotency key so a retried webhook/callback never extends the period
// twice. The Alipay rail ALSO writes an AlipayOrder (the gateway callback looks
// it up); this row is the unified renewal audit. See docs/design-spec-settings-redesign.md.
model SubscriptionRenewal {
  id           String    @id @default(cuid())
  userId       String
  rail         String // 'stripe' | 'alipay'
